{"tid":991643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日便利店為奧運禁售成人雜誌","createTime":"2019-01-22T13:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T13:00:00.000Z","uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb74898873b235b781bc218cfe867654ac481e80","tid":991643,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:49:32.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=AqY7y7jJ%2FuWEOQGpCgMhp5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8027333a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】為了迎接2020東京奧運，日本便利店即將停售成人雜誌。<br />\n<br />\n便利店龍頭7-11周二表示，將由今年夏天開始在日本停售成人雜誌，意味著外國旅客於今年9月，前往欣賞欖球世界盃，便無法再在便利店購買相關刊物。這決定是因日本便利店要照顧較多的女性和青少年等顧客，而且大賽前後也有大批外國遊客湧入，即使24小時便利店會出售各種各類的商品，但不少外國人仍對便利店出售成人雜誌感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n全日本，單是7-11便利店已超過2萬間，其中5000間一直有售賣相關刊物，但佔總銷售額低於1%，發言人認為對業績影響輕微：「日本即將會舉行國際大賽，但其實只是其中一個停售因素，並非全部，現代人對便利店的印象已隨時代有所不同。」"},{"pid":"bf693ae1504cea76fa3c6ecf31eb37e3b9f99fdf","tid":991643,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:51:15.000Z","msg":"去便利店蛇王睇雜誌既日子結束了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e5f32123e6ebec7ec9dd47b71fb09c555c3bd2","tid":991643,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"不過照有雞叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4732db64c372173afebe4d89a13d77c5c1190834","tid":991643,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4eb573f854ea8a5f34b5437207f3c77063bbf9e","tid":991643,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf693ae1504cea76fa3c6ecf31eb37e3b9f99fdf","tid":991643,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:51:15.000Z","msg":"去便利店蛇王睇雜誌既日子結束了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.g